                <p class="paragraph--2"><b>“<em>On a technical level, the solution offers strong support for all the Windows and Linux operating systems in use across our business, including a number of legacy systems that would have posed significant difficulties for other technologies we considered. Most importantly, the Qualys solution can scan systems while they are running and present the findings in easy-to-digest dashboards for rapid analysis and action by our teams.</em>”</b></p>

				<h2 class="heading--2">Gaining 360-degree visibility</h2>
                <p class="paragraph--2">Using Qualys Vulnerability Management with the lightweight Qualys Cloud Agent, WINDTRE has
